data.description: Handyman special!! This ranch-style home, located at 603 North Pryor Cove Road, sits on a private road with mountain views, offering tranquility and privacy. Set on a spacious one-acre lot, this property is a perfect blend of country living and city convenience. 3 Bedrooms, 1 Bath with a second bathroom currently under construction provides ample space for comfortable living, with a layout designed for both functionality and style.A 3-Car Garage and two outbuildings allow plenty of room for your vehicles, hobbies, or extra storage. A car enthusiast's dream! or a mechanic work-from-home garage.As-is conventional/cash loan only
